So if the first part of my talk appealed to you,

00:18:55.040 --> 00:18:57.839
you just wanna try out OJS for the first time,

00:18:57.839 --> 00:18:59.920
get your first bar plot in or whatever it is,

00:19:00.479 --> 00:19:02.239
check out the quartered documentation

00:19:02.239 --> 00:19:04.800
or check out observable plot and observable inputs

00:19:04.800 --> 00:19:06.560
because they both have great documentation.

00:19:08.479 --> 00:19:11.119
If the intermediate part interested you,

00:19:11.119 --> 00:19:13.439
you're starting to get a bit more adventurous with OJS,

00:19:13.439 --> 00:19:14.959
check out observables examples.

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.520
But also at 360info on our GitHub,

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:20.239
