00:19:24.880 --> 00:19:25.839
So please check them.

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:30.000
And if you were interested in the last part with Sferto

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:31.760
and Svelte, please do check out Sferto.

00:19:31.760 --> 00:19:32.719
I'd love for you to use it.

00:19:33.439 --> 00:19:35.280
I also highly recommend a blog post

